title: IAA Tonight | Jimmy G to the Browns? AND Minnesota Vikings Season Preview
description: The San Francisco 49ers have been trying to trade Jimmy Garoppolo all offseason and haven't found a suitor yet, but with Deshaun Watson's looming suspension possibly for the entire season, should the Browns pursue Jimmy G? Plus, we continue our Countdown to Kickoff with the Minnesota Vikings. Will Captain Kirk lead the ship to a NFC North division title?
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, Ashley Nicole Moss, Chantel Tremetiere)
